   241→    /**
   242→     * The {@link RecordBatch batch} of {@link Record records} is converted to a {@link List list} of
   243→     * {@link ConsumerRecord consumer records} and returned. {@link BufferSupplier Decompression} and
   244→     * {@link Deserializer deserialization} of the {@link Record record's} key and value are performed in
